          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-1" n="1">Dear Dean<lb/>|Since in Cruxes and Puns You and I deal</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-2" n="2">Pray why is a Woman a Sive and a Riddle?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-3" n="3">'Tis a thought that came into My Noddle this morning</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-4" n="4">In Bed as I lay, S<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>, a Tossing and Turning</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-5" n="5">You'll find if You read but a few of Your Histories</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-6" n="6">All Women as Eve, all Women are Mysteries.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-7" n="7">To Find out this Riddle I know You'll be eager</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-8" n="8">And make Ev'ry One of the Sex a Bell-phager;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-9" n="9">But that will not do for I mean to Commend them</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-10" n="10">I swear without Iest I an honour intend 'em.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-11" n="11">In a Sieve S<hi rend="superscript">ṛ</hi> their Ancient Extraction I quite tell,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-12" n="12">In a Riddle I give You their Pow'r and their Title.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-13" n="13">This I told You before, Do You know what I mean S<hi rend="superscript">ṛ</hi></l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-14" n="14">Not I by my Troth S<hi rend="superscript">ṛ</hi>── then read it again Sir</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-15" n="15">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-16" n="16">om.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-17" n="17">The reason I send you these Lines of Rhymes double</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-18" n="18">Is purely in Pitty to save You the Trouble</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-19" n="19">Of thinking Two hours for a Rhyme as You did last</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-20" n="20">When Your Pegasus Canter'd in Tripple and rid fast</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-21" n="21">As for My little Nagg, which I keep att Parnassus</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-22" n="22">With Phœbus's Leave to run with his Asses;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-23" n="23">He goes slow and sure, and he never is Iaded</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-24" n="24">While your Fiery Steed is Whip'd, spurr'd, Bastinaded.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-971-002D-line-25" n="25">«LD»T: Sheridan</l>
          </lg>
